sql.up: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS blog  (id uuid   primary key   default (gen_random_uuid () )  not null  , title varchar (2048)  not null  , description text   not null  , content json   not null  , tags json   default (('[]')::json )  not null  , "categoryId" uuid  , "thumbnailId" uuid  , "authorId" uuid   not null  , "lastEditorId" uuid  , visibility "visibility"   default ('draft')  not null  , pinned boolean   default (false)  not null  )
